<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">غ ل م:</span> <span class="c2">(الْغُلَامُ)</span> مَعْرُوفٌ وَجَمْعُهُ <span class="c2">(غِلْمَةٌ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(غِلْمَانٌ)</span> .<span class="c5"> وَيُقَالُ:</span> <span class="c2">(غُلَامٌ)</span> بَيِّنُ <span class="c2">(الْغُلُومَةِ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(الْغُلُومِيَّةِ)</span> وَالْأُنْثَى <span class="c2">(غُلَامَةٌ)</span> .<span class="c5"> قَالَ يَصِفُ فَرَسًا:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
